New Records: The Chicago White Sox are on track to reach 117 losses, matching a post-1900 record
Key Match Events: Jordyn Adams' walk-off single in the 13th inning to give the Los Angeles Angels a 4-3 victory
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game went into extra innings with both teams scoring in the 10th and 12th innings; the Angels had the bases loaded in the 10th and 12th innings but finally won in the 13th; this was the fifth walk-off victory for the Angels this season
